<pc>，</pc>以右司諫韓璜党富直柔<pc>，</pc>責監潯州稅<pc>。</pc>張琪伏誅<pc>。</pc>
<num value="47">庚戌</num>
<pc>，</pc>富直柔罷<pc>。</pc>荊湖<pc>、</pc>廣西<term>宣撫使</term>吳敏始受命置司柳州<pc>。</pc>
<num value="48">辛亥</num>
<pc>，</pc>升<placeName>康州</placeName>為德慶府<pc>。</pc>
<num value="49">壬子</num>
<pc>，</pc>詔內外侍從各舉所知<measure quantity="3" unit="people">
<num value="3">三</num>人</measure>
<pc>。</pc>
