<placeName>蔡州</placeName>褒信縣弓手許約叛<pc>，</pc>據<placeName>光州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
<placeName>階州</placeName>安撫孫注複洮州<pc>。</pc>龔富等圍南<placeName>劍州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
